{
  "texts": [
    "We compare the planning rounds of AUTOACT with various baselines.",
    "The win rate of each method is listed in Fig. 6 and comprehensive analysis can be found in §5.",
    "Here we present the average planning rounds of various methods on HotpotQA with Llama-2-70B-chat in Tab. 5.",
    "Note that to maintain fairness, we exclude the planning steps related to reflection of AUTOACT.",
    "Task Name: HotpotQA Task Description: This is a question-answering task that includes high-quality multi-hop questions."
  ]
}